{
  "stem": "13911.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is why I-- my sleepless nights, because suddenly everything is so graphic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Suddenly I see and I hear, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Before, in the earlier years, I-- I kept myself from thinking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I knew it happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No idea.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Like, I-- I forbid myself to-- to be graphic in my mind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, it's graphic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's graphic, and it's audible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I can see how they round the-- the graves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They see the graves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and-- and women, men, children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "At that time, and in those days, you were especially, very modest, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "To run naked and-- and-- and then children crying, and babies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know/",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you have to jump, yet, in the grave, and then be shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which-- which again, I know exactly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not from hearing because on one of the-- [SIGHS] one of the-- the work, the forced labor-- oh, my mind is getting-- Forced labor, there was that German.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name was Keller.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Herr Keller.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Keller.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Drunk, they were all drunk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, having a good time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And also, it was-- it helped to cope with everything, easier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and as we are doing the work in that bombed-out house, he is sitting and grinning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, I killed-- What did he say? 10,000 Jews I shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was getting 30 [NON-ENGLISH], let's say $0.30, for each head.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know, I know because I'll tell you later, again, when we get to it, how I know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw it with my two eyes, anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they undressed naked, leave the clothes behind, because they better make use of it, the Germans, and jump with your children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To see your own children jumping.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, jumping, not just standing and shoot me.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
